1360.name: Nicro FM 53MD Tig
1360.Applications: Nicro FM 53MD is used for the gas-tungsten-arc and gas-metal-arc welding of INCONEL alloy 693, and the overlaying of carbon steels and stainless steels to provide a nickel-chromium-aluminum alloy corrosion resistant surface.
1360.Suitable_For: Cladding against high temperature, radiant heater tubes, furnace rolls, muffles in bright annealing furnaces (H2 atmosphere), rotary kilns, pipe hangers, waste gas components, hydrogen production, methanol and ammonia synthesis, Inconel alloy 693
